{"tid":1290991,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"喂 點知你係咪社工呀？ 入黎認識一下社工","createTime":"2019-07-06T16:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T14:23:36.000Z","uid":78885,"like":92,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1aefd2f8b04f70a0db794c34fbe30550295d90d5","tid":1290991,"uid":78885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:41:58.000Z","msg":"我發現原來好多人都唔認識社工<br />\n所以請你花30秒睇一睇下面<br />\n<br />\n所有已註冊既社工係一定一定有呢張證<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1iEHuF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1iEHuF.png&h=33821614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n證上面有<br />\n1 名(中英)<br />\n2. 註冊編號<br />\n3. 註冊期滿日期<br />\n4. 註冊類別<br />\n5. 註冊所基於的資格<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記得記得要睇清楚名同埋註冊期滿日期有無過期</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n各位街坊記得要一齊捍衛社工既專業呀！<br />\n你亦都有權要佢出示張證！<br />\n根據《社會工作者註冊條例》，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>冒充註冊社工亦屬違法</strong></span></span>，一經定罪，亦可處第五級罰款（五萬元）。"},{"pid":"a41fc22e376402ef4dde392254e6374283ef5f30","tid":1290991,"uid":78885,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:43:25.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"f0372139cbc01803722c9a25926189a02c7bf2af","tid":1290991,"uid":164374,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:43:41.000Z","msg":"以後有人再自稱社工, 要佢出示証件, 冒認社工不得好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc6f7d3b181b26b441537f9beacc12baf08aeb2","tid":1290991,"uid":78885,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:45:18.000Z","msg":"邊個社工要帶服務使用者去參加示威咁夠膽呀????"},{"pid":"66f655ec98616bebde9d69a939509bd3fc042f25","tid":1290991,"uid":1247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:45:59.000Z","msg":"有過一絲 狗冒社工引你去講發夢內容再去拘捕你 既念頭"},{"pid":"029129b1e8294a9b51c4076aa42049363aaf4d2c","tid":1290991,"uid":78885,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"66f655e